Title: How many invoices are still oustanding for customer jeff's jalopies as of (date)?
QueryBody: select count(distinct transaction_id) from master_txn_table where customers = "jeff's jalopies" and transaction_type = 'invoice' and AR_paid = 'unpaid'

Title: Since This quarter, how many invoices have been late?
QueryBody: select count(distinct transaction_id) from master_txn_table where transaction_type = 'invoice' and due_date < current_date and transaction_date BETWEEN date(current_date) AND date(current_date)  and open_balance > 0

Title: How much money did we make between <date> and <date>?
QueryBody: select sum(credit) from master_txn_table  as T1 join chart_of_accounts as T2 on T1.account = T2.account_name where account_type in ('Income','Other Income') and transaction_date BETWEEN date(current_date) AND date(current_date)

Title: What was the highest bill rondonuwu fruit and vegi received from lee advertising?
QueryBody: select max(credit) from master_txn_table where customers = "rondonuwu fruit and vegi" and transaction_type = 'bill' and vendor = "lee advertising"

Title: How many meals did we deliver last week?
QueryBody: select sum(debit) from master_txn_table  as T1 join chart_of_accounts as T2 on T1.account = T2.account_name where instr(account,'medical & health') and strftime("%W", transaction_date) = strftime("%W", current_timestamp) and strftime("%Y", transaction_date) = strftime("%Y", current_timestamp) and account_type in ('Expense','Other Expense')

Title: How much money have we paid to met life dental Last 30 days?
QueryBody: select sum(debit) from master_txn_table as T1 join chart_of_accounts as T2 on T1.account = T2.account_name where account_type in ('Expense', 'Other Expense') and vendor = "met life dental" and transaction_date BETWEEN date( current_date, "-30 days") AND date( current_date)

Title: show me expenses for permit this week
QueryBody: select sum(debit) from master_txn_table  as T1 join chart_of_accounts as T2 on T1.account = T2.account_name where instr(account,'medical & health') and strftime("%W", transaction_date) = strftime("%W", current_timestamp) and strftime("%Y", transaction_date) = strftime("%Y", current_timestamp) and account_type in ('Expense','Other Expense')

Title: What is my average invoice from 55 twin lane?
QueryBody: select avg(amount) from (select distinct transaction_id, amount from master_txn_table where customers = "55 twin lane")

Title: how much did we spend with united state treasury on cost of labor
QueryBody: select sum(debit) from master_txn_table as T1 join chart_of_accounts as T2 on T1.account = T2.account_name where account_type in ('Expense', 'Other Expense') and instr(account,"cost of labor") and vendor = "united state treasury"

Title: What our monthly spend on edd
QueryBody: select sum(debit) from master_txn_table where vendor = "edd" group by strftime("%m", transaction_date);

Title: How much did we pay mahoney mug the This month?
QueryBody: select sum(debit) from master_txn_table as T1 join chart_of_accounts as T2 on T1.account = T2.account_name where account_type in ('Expense', 'Other Expense') and vendor = "mahoney mug" and transaction_date BETWEEN date( current_date, "start of month") AND date( current_date)

Title: When was the last time we billed for rock
QueryBody: select transaction_date from master_txn_table  as T1 join chart_of_accounts as T2 on T1.account = T2.account_name where account_type in ('Income','Other Income') and product_service = "rock" order by transaction_date desc limit 1

Title: Compare sales by customer year to date
QueryBody: select customers, sum(credit) from master_txn_table where account in ('Income','Other Income') and strftime("%Y", transaction_date) = strftime("%Y", current_date) group by customers

Title: What are my account payable Last 12 months?
QueryBody: select sum(credit) from master_txn_table where account = 'account payable' and transaction_date BETWEEN date( current_date, "-12 months", "start of month") AND date( current_date)

Title: This week, what was our largest expense?
QueryBody: select account, sum(debit) from master_txn_table  as T1 join chart_of_accounts as T2 on T1.account = T2.account_name where account_type in ('Expense','Other Expense') and transaction_date BETWEEN date( current_date, "weekday 0", "-7 days") AND date( current_date)  order by sum(debit) desc limit 1

Title: How many invoices are still oustanding for freeman sporting goods as of yesterday?
QueryBody: select count(distinct transaction_id) from master_txn_table where customers = "freeman sporting goods" and transaction_type = 'invoice' and open_balance >0 and transaction_date date( current_date, "-1 days")

Title: What were my expenses in the This week to date?
QueryBody: select sum(debit) from master_txn_table as T1 join chart_of_accounts as T2 on T1.account = T2.account_name where transaction_date BETWEEN date( current_date, "weekday 0", "-7 days") AND date( current_date)  and account_type in ('Expense','Other Expense')

Title: what was our top 3 selling products and their sales in q1
QueryBody: select product_service, sum(quantity) from master_txn_table as T1 join chart_of_accounts as T2 on T1.account = T2.account_name where account_type in ('Income', 'Other Income') and strftime("%m", transaction_date) in ("01", "02", "03") group by product_service order by sum(quantity) desc limit 3;

Title: In the on <date>, how many rocks did amy's bird sanctuary sell?
QueryBody: select sum(quantity) from master_txn_table where customers = "amy's bird sanctuary" and product_service = "rocks" and transaction_date BETWEEN date(current_date) AND date(current_date)

Title: How many hour did 0969 ocean view road sell This month to date?
QueryBody: select sum(quantity) from master_txn_table where customers = "0969 ocean view road" and product_service = "hour" and transaction_date BETWEEN date( current_date, "start of month") AND date( current_date)

Title: What was the total amount collected in "Bond Fees" yesterday?
QueryBody: select sum(credit) from master_txn_table where account in ('Income','Other Income') and transaction_date = date(current_date, "-1 days") and product_service = 'Bond fees'

Title: What was our total spend for other income in last 12 months
QueryBody: select sum(debit) from master_txn_table  as T1 join chart_of_accounts as T2 on T1.account = T2.account_name where instr(account,"other income") and strftime("%m", transaction_date) >= strftime("%m", current_timestamp) - 12 and account_type in ('Expense','Other Expense')

Title: What's the profit for the aug?
QueryBody: select sum(credit - debit) from master_txn_table  as T1 join chart_of_accounts as T2 on T1.account = T2.account_name where account_type in ('Income','Other Income','Expense','Other Expense') and strftime("%m", transaction_date) = 8

Title: Who are my outstanding debtors?
QueryBody: select customer_name, balance from customers where balance != 0

Title: What are my total project costs for Project XYZ?

Title: MTD, what are my AR?

Title: Who are my outstanding creditors?

Title: Last 12 months, what are my account receivable?

Title: What's the last journal entry that dylan sollfrank recorded?
QueryBody: select * from journal_entry where customer_name = "dylan sollfrank" order by transaction_date desc limit 1

Title: What acount had our biggest expense yesterday?
QueryBody: select account, sum(debit) from master_txn_table as T1 join chart_of_accounts as T2 on T1.account = T2.account_name  where account_type in ('Expense','Other Expense') and date(transaction_date) = date(current_date) - 1 group by account order by sum(debit) desc limit 1

Title: Show all of sonnenschein family store's transactions
QueryBody: select distinct transaction_id from master_txn_table where customers = "sonnenschein family store"

Title: YTD, how much did we pay cigna health care?
QueryBody: select sum(debit) from master_txn_table as T1 join chart_of_accounts as T2 on T1.account = T2.account_name where account_type in ('Expense', 'Other Expense') and vendor = "cigna health care" and transaction_date BETWEEN date(current_date) AND date(current_date)

Title: What was my expense by products in may?
QueryBody: select product_service, sum(debit) from master_txn_table  as T1 join chart_of_accounts as T2 on T1.account = T2.account_name where strftime("%m", transaction_date) = 5 and account_type in ('Expense','Other Expense') group by product_service

Title: How many MASTERCARD transactions did we have yesterday?
QueryBody: select count(distinct transaction_id) from master_txn_table where payment_method = 'mastercard'

Title: What payment method was used to pay sales receipt #101010
QueryBody: select payment_method from master_txn_table where transaction_type = 'sales receipt' and transaction_id = "101010"

Title: What was the most recent invoice for rago travel agency?
QueryBody: select transaction_id from master_txn_table where transaction_type = 'invoice' and customers = "rago travel agency" order by transaction_date desc limit 1

Title: what customers are buying less than last month
QueryBody: select T1.customers, revenue_this_month, revenue_last_month from (select customers, sum(credit) as revenue_this_month from master_txn_table   as T1 join chart_of_accounts as T2 on T1.account = T2.account_name where account_type in ('Income','Other Income') and strftime("%m", transaction_date) = strftime("%m", current_timestamp) group by customers) as T1 join (select customers, sum(credit) as revenue_last_month from master_txn_table   as T1 join chart_of_accounts as T2 on T1.account = T2.account_name where account_type in ('Income','Other Income') and strftime("%m", transaction_date) = strftime("%m", current_timestamp) - 1 group by customers) as T2 on T1.customers = T2.customers where revenue_this_month < revenue_last_month

Title: Since This year, how many invoices have been past due?
QueryBody: select count(distinct transaction_id) from master_txn_table where transaction_type = 'invoice' and due_date < current_date and transaction_date BETWEEN date(current_date, 'start of year') AND date(current_date) and open_balance > 0

Title: When was the first time we billed for bank charge?
QueryBody: select transaction_date from master_txn_table where transaction_type = 'bill' and instr(account,"bank charge") order by transaction_date limit 1

Title: What are sushi by katsuyuki recurring product purchases over past 6 months?
QueryBody: select product_service from ( select product_service, count(distinct strftime("%m", transaction_date)) as n_months from master_txn_table where customers = "sushi by katsuyuki" and strftime("%m", transaction_date) >= strftime("%m", current_date) - 6 group by product_service ) where n_months >= 6
